features: Case Size - 6.3 x 6.1 inch, fits most standard sized glasses, sunglasses, computer glasses and more.
Protective - Soft and smooth material makes it free from scratches on the surface of your glasses, and the spacious design is perfect even for over-sized glasses.

Convenient - Put the glass in the case and fixed the temple to the back strap, then close the buckle. With sturdy carabiner, you can easily attach it to a belt loop, a backpack, a purse. No burden to your trip.

Stylish Glass Holder - Available in a variety of vibrant fashion designs to suit for your taste. Perfect for the chic business men and woman, the stylish student, the bold trendsetter. Great gift for Birthday, Back to School, Halloween, Thanksgiving and Christmas.
After Sales - We believe in our products and customer service, for any questions or concerns please contact us without hesitation.
description: Wearing glasses these days is more than a necessity to improve your eyesight. They are also considered to be amazing accessories to coordinate with your outfits. If your sunglasses are your tastement pieces and essential everyday accessory, why not make sure you can find them at all times and that they are kept in a fashionable case? This Eyeglasses Case is a perfect companion for eyeglass wearers. Whether you’re climbing a mountain, lounging at the beach, hanging out at a picnic, or just reading at home, this carrying case keeps everything within easy reach and protected.
Size: 6.3 x 6.1 Inch / 16x15.5 cm Weight: 50g Material: PU Leather
Buckle Closure /Handy Carabiner/Soft and Light Material
Suitable for most standard sized Glasses, Eyeglass, Sunglasses, Computer Glasses Sports Goggles and more.
Fashion and Stylish design, say goodbye to monotonous traditional glasses case.
